    "Name": "Great Wyrm",
    "Details": "Produced during the Jihad in 3069, this variant utilizes new innovations introduced just prior to the war. The dual UAC/2s have been removed in favor of a HAG 20 with two tons of ammunition. The LRM-10 launcher and ER small lasers have also been removed. In their place, a third ER medium laser has been added, along with an AP Gauss rifle with one ton of ammunition. The armor protection has been increased, with standard armor exchanged for ferro-fibrous armor.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.07</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Upper</color>",
